== Documentation ==
This is to be used when a page is a stub and needs more additions.
=== Example Usage ===
<nowiki>{{Stub|Some sections are missing content}}</nowiki>

will make:
{{Stub|Some sections are missing content|nocat=1}}

=== Template parameters ===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Name !! Variable !! Description
|-
| Reason || <code>1</code>|| Gives the reason as to why the page is considered a stub.
|}
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"1": {
			"label": "Reason",
			"description": "Why is this page a stub?",
			"type": "string",
			"suggested": true
		}
	},
	"description": "When a page needs more information"
}
</templatedata>
